text.tspan: Frameworks have become quite popular. Generally speaking, this is a good thing. There
are many frameworks out there that are free, powerful, and useful.
However, frameworks are not architecturesthough some try to be.
Most framework authors offer their work for free because they want to be helpful to the
community. They want to give back. This is laudable. However, regardless of their high-
minded motives, those authors do not have
best interests at heart. They cant,
because they dont know you, and they dont know your problems.
